com.adp.marketplace.connection.configuration

Class ConnectionConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adp.marketplace.connection.configuration.ConnectionConfiguration
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuthorizationCodeConfiguration, ClientCredentialsConfiguration

    public abstract class ConnectionConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object

    ConnectionConfiguration is the abstract base class for all grant types GrantType which allows an application to configure connections ADPAPIConnection based on OAuth2.0 recognized Grant Types.

    Author:
    tallaprs
